\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {7.2}{\ignorespaces The RNN unrolled across three time steps. The recurrence $\mathbf  {h}_t = g(W_x \mathbf  {x}_t + W_h \mathbf  {h}_{t-1} + \mathbf  {b})$ applies the same parameter matrices at every step. Training by BPTT requires propagating gradients through the full unrolled graph; for a dependency spanning $k$ steps, this involves a product of $k$ Jacobians that decays or explodes exponentially.}}{61}{figure.caption.20}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:rnn_unrolled}{{7.2}{61}{The RNN unrolled across three time steps. The recurrence $\mathbf {h}_t = g(W_x \mathbf {x}_t + W_h \mathbf {h}_{t-1} + \mathbf {b})$ applies the same parameter matrices at every step. Training by BPTT requires propagating gradients through the full unrolled graph; for a dependency spanning $k$ steps, this involves a product of $k$ Jacobians that decays or explodes exponentially}{figure.caption.20}{}}
